$ VIM: src/feature.h
@ src/feature.h

`feature.h` allows to define some preferences for → development/vim. In order to change these preferences, it should be changed
before → development/vim/compiling[compiling vim].

{ Definitions of vimrc / startup-initialization files

  Some macros are
    • `VIMRC_FILE`
    • `GVIMRC_FILE`
    • `EXREC_FILE`
    • `USR_VIMRC_FILE`
    • `USR_VIMRC_FILE2`
    • `USR_VIMRC_FILE3`

}
{ VIM_DEFAULTS_FILE

  → development/vim/runtime/defaults_vim

}
{ RUNTIME_DIRNAME

   Stores the (generic, whatever that is) name of the → development/vim/sources/runtime[runtime] files.

   The value of `RUNTIME_DIRNAME` is used in → development/vim/sources/src/misc1_c#vim-src-misc1-vim_version_dir[`vim_version_dir()`].

}

sa:
  → development/vim/features
